Waktu melukis sudah selesai.

151
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,320
Tolong tampilkan lukisan kalian.

152
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:42,600
Aku…

153
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:43,600
Aku tidak sengaja!

154
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,720
Untung bajuku tidak kotor.

155
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,400
Maniak kebersihan ini.

156
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:23,840
Apa ini?

157
