550
00:31:48,080 --> 00:31:49,040
Janji apa?

551
00:31:50,280 --> 00:31:51,480
Kau tidak ingat?

552
00:31:54,080 --> 00:31:55,200
Beberapa saat lalu
karena terlalu nakal,

553
00:31:55,680 --> 00:31:57,840
