554
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:58,680
Aku lupa semuanya.

555
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:01,240
Ternyata begitu.

556
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:03,360
Tapi, aku dengar dari Xiao Ai,

557
00:32:03,600 --> 00:32:05,480
